{"tid":2366880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[慎入] 可憐男頭部長滿巨大粉瘤　醫師擠出超噁「沙拉蛋膿湯」","createTime":"2021-01-15T02:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T10:23:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4118a0156be11df33a4abcc3d7befac6a5640e","tid":2366880,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"美國知名「戰痘醫師」(Dr.Pimple Popper)、皮膚科醫師桑德拉‧李(Sandra Lee)，近日又分享一個特殊病例，這名67歲男病患丹尼斯(Dennis)，頭部長滿多顆巨大粉瘤，而且已經在他頭上長了超過20年。丹尼斯近日找桑德拉診治，丹尼斯的狀況，連桑德拉都感到不可思議。<br />\n<br />\n來自密西根的丹尼斯，罹患的就是俗稱粉瘤的皮脂腺囊腫(Sebaceous cyst)，他承認這些粉瘤在他頭上，已經長了超過20年，而且越長越大。這些巨大粉瘤，也造成他生活上的種種不便，包括睡覺時若不小心壓到，就會感到疼痛、不舒服。此外，喜歡騎機車的丹尼斯，也無法戴安全帽。他的妻子多娜(Donna)看到丈夫的狀況，非常擔心，她很害怕若丹尼斯再不醫治，很快就會離開她的身邊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210115/LXPFP7GDUZDXBNY6UEC66EG4PE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210115%2FLXPFP7GDUZDXBNY6UEC66EG4PE%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=8b7c337a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210115%2FLXPFP7GDUZDXBNY6UEC66EG4PE%2F&h=74d25557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210115/LXPFP7GDUZDXBNY6UEC66EG4PE/</a>"},{"pid":"fa8e7a09e1e812b03889ae6c9edd8746dbcc7785","tid":2366880,"uid":174013,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"春袋生上頭"},{"pid":"36a7e3df23af76969d08345ad59a3ab05e2562ba","tid":2366880,"uid":31323,"like":105,"dislike":1,"score":104,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲post就有圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865a5c2f8d5dc44405b2f0bd84e5c20a48e54489","tid":2366880,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"壽星公"},{"pid":"0b7f2792fbdf084c375224ca872f362d3f30be89","tid":23